data.description: Welcome to the picturesque neighborhood of Lyndhurst. One of Covington's well-sought-after communities. Situated on 1.070 acres of complete serenity, this traditional-style three-side brick Ranch home offers comfort and endless opportunities for relaxation and recreation. 4 Bedrooms, 3.5 baths, Hardwood flooring throughout the main level, a Separate living room, a Dining room with coffered ceiling, a Kitchen, stainless appliances, including double ovens, wine cooler, granite countertops, overlooks a large family/keeping room complement with vaulted ceilings and fireplace. The roommate floor plan adds a sense of privacy. The owner's spacious suite is enhanced with an Architectural ceiling and a fireplace. The upstairs bedroom/bonus room may be used as a teen/in-law/office/ fitness/wellness room. The space in the basement is jaw-dropping! A blank canvas of approx. 2,904 sq ft waits for your dream design. Amenities include a clubhouse, fishing opportunities, a fitness center, a homeowners association, a serene lake, and more! Sold AS-IS.
